    "text": "College Affordability and Innovation Act of 2018\n\nThis bill provides incentives\u00a0for institutions of higher education (IHEs) that receive federal financial aid to: (1) provide programs designed to decrease the cost and time required to obtain postsecondary degrees or certificates; and (2) meet accountability standards that focus on affordability, accessibility for low- and middle-income students, and value."
